Usage: rename_obj [-help]
                  <inst|hInst|vCell|topCell|term|hTerm|hNet|test_clock|test_clock_domain>
                  <new_name> [-escape_ok] [-flexible] [-quiet]

-help          # Prints out the command usage
<inst|hInst|vCell|topCell|term|hTerm|hNet|test_clock|test_clock_domain>
               # Object to rename ((inst|hInst|vCell|topCell|term|hTerm|hNet|test_clock|test_clock_domain), required)
<new_name>     # New base_name for object (string, required)
-escape_ok     # Automatically escape special characters in <new_name>
               # (bool, optional)
-flexible      # Fix name collisions by adding _1, _2, etc. suffix
               # (bool, optional)
-quiet         # Suppress messages about renamed objects (bool, optional)